  <span id="freeText16006385691143914716" style="display:none">Not even sure if it makes 3 stars.<br><br>Most of the Linda Howard books I have read have been solid 4 or 5 stars. This one did not make the grade. Found it a bit too like the Outlander books which cannot be trumped in my opinion. Same premise. Time travel, Highlands of Scotland.<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1415789243i/11846064._SY540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br>I really cannot muster up much enthusiasm to write a full review.<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1415789243i/11846065.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br> <b>The human heart had the capacity to love many people ...</b><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1415789243i/11846066.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"></span>
